e\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pdm1665702915368.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pdm1665702915368.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pdm1665702915368.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pdm1665702915368\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n               \n Field Definitions\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"pdm1665702915368__field_definitions_360500\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">When defining fields, you can specify the field interface, syntax, and layout definitions, either directly or in a template.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pdm1665702915368__p_d111674e1_d111675e1_d111676e1\">The following topics summarize the codes you can use in these definitions:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pdm1665702915368__li_d42860e1_d42861e1_d42862e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ubb1665702556881.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ubb1665702556881.html\" title=\"A field interface code is specified in the field's Database Interface property, and determines how the data is stored in the database. The code defines the packing code and field length, as well numeric decimal and scaling options.\">Field Interface Codes</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pdm1665702915368__li_d42863e1_d42864e1_d42865e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jjg1714304600909.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jjg1714304600909.html\" title=\"Field syntax codes specify the data entry pattern, the allowed characters, and whether fields are mandatory or read-only.\">Field Syntax Codes</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pdm1665702915368__li_d42866e1_d42867e1_d42868e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iha1665702711837.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iha1665702711837.html\" title=\"Field layout codes specify how data is formatted for display. When multiple codes are specified, they must be separated by commas.\">Field Layout Codes</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pdm1665702915368__li_d42869e1_d42870e1_d42871e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ckh1665702551507.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ckh1665702551507.html\" title=\"Display formats control the way the data is displayed, as opposed to the way it is stored.\">Display Formats</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530880\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530880\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Field Definitions Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Field Definitions When defining fields, you can specify the field interface, syntax, and layout definitions, either directly or in a template. The following topics summarize the codes you can use in these definitions: Field Interface Codes Field Syntax Codes Field Layout Codes Display Formats Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}